description: I was in the mood for some young athletes today. I went to an indoor swimming pool and waited outside for any attractive boys leaving the building. After a very long time, I finally met a real cutie. He was a college student and was on his way to a lecture. I had to convince him fast or risk losing this amazing opportunity. He had a part-time job so I had to give him a good enough offer. The boy surprised me. He liked the money and was quite crazy. Of course he was shy but still he undressed right in public. Too bad I also wanted things that couldn´t be done in the street. He reluctantly agreed to accompany me to a rooftop garage, where things got a lot naughtier. The boy sucked me off nicely so I decided to offer him all my money, I wanted his ass whatever the cost.
title: Czech Hunter 374
